        </table></div><div class="header-trail" style="font-size: 12px"><div title="trail"><a href="?keys=FGEA-print&amp;mode=TOC">The Founding Era Collection</a>&gt; <a href="?keys=ADMS-print&amp;mode=TOC">The Adams Papers Digital Edition</a>&gt; <a href="?keys=ADMS-print-06&amp;mode=TOC">Papers of John Adams</a>&gt; <a href="?keys=ADMS-print-06-09&amp;mode=TOC">Volume 9, March 1780July 1780</a>&gt; <a href="?keys=ADMS-print-06-09-02&amp;mode=TOC">Papers of John Adams</a>&gt; From William Lee, 30 March 1780</div></div></div></div><div class="body-norm entry"><div class="printable-document"><a href="/founders/default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-09-02-0069&amp;printable=yes" style="font-weight:normal"><img style="border:0; vertical-align:text-bottom;" src="/img-ML/document-print.png" alt=""/> printable version</a><div class="header-arrows"><div class="header-comp-C1"><a class="point-prev" href="?keys=ADMS-print-06-09-02-0068" title="To the President of Congress, No. 31, 30 March 1780"></a></div><div class="header-comp-C2"></div><div class="header-comp-C3"><a class="point-next" href="?keys=ADMS-print-06-09-02-0070" title="From the Comte de Vergennes [document with translation]"></a></div></div><form style="display:inline" action="Utilities/goto-page-in-current-volume.xqy">
